  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cancellable async operations with AbortController integration",
    "Pausable and resumable execution via generator-based control flow",
    "Composable concurrency primitives: all, race, allSettled, scope, and withConcurrencyLimit",
    "Background execution using requestIdleCallback",
    "First-class support for async/sync iterables, streams, and generators",
    "Automatic resource management via Explicit Resource Management (using/await using)",
    "Built-in deadline and timeout enforcement",
    "Stream splitting by value or predicate",
    "Promise-compatible: supports then/catch/finally and await syntax",
    "Multi-runtime: Deno, Node.js, Bun, Cloudflare Workers, and browsers"
  ],
